Package org.thingsboard.server.queue.provider

Interface TbCoreQueueFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TbUsageStatsClientQueueFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AwsSqsMonolithQueueFactory, AwsSqsTbCoreQueueFactory, InMemoryMonolithQueueFactory, KafkaMonolithQueueFactory, KafkaTbCoreQueueFactory, PubSubMonolithQueueFactory, PubSubTbCoreQueueFactory, RabbitMqMonolithQueueFactory, RabbitMqTbCoreQueueFactory, ServiceBusMonolithQueueFactory, ServiceBusTbCoreQueueFactory
    public interface TbCoreQueueFactory
extends TbUsageStatsClientQueueFactory
    Responsible for initialization of various Producers and Consumers used by TB Core Node. Implementation Depends on the queue queue.type from yml or TB_QUEUE_TYPE environment variable
